1. *Menja* se vreme u toku dana. (The weather is changing throughout the day.)
2. On *menja* svoje mišljenje često. (He changes his mind often.)
3. Ona *menja* boje kose. (She changes her hair color.)
4. *Menjanje* mode je neprekidno. (Fashion changes are continuous.)
5. *Menjaše* se ukuse tokom godina. (Tastes changed over the years.)